        "label": "Vimeo OAuth app credentials and access tokens",
        "generateUrl": "https://developer.vimeo.com/apps",
        "setup": "Create an app on the [My Apps](https://developer.vimeo.com/apps) page, then open the app to get its `client_id` and `client_secret`. From that app page you can also **Generate an access token** for your own account, or use the OAuth 2.0 flows described in [Working with Authentication](https://developer.vimeo.com/api/authentication) to obtain access tokens for public or private data. Vimeo says all API authentication is based on OAuth 2.0, with supported grant types including client credentials, authorization code, implicit, and device code."
      }
